title: Wrong data set result returned when an invalid filter expression is set for row[0]
description: When I set a filter expression like 'row[0] equals to 0', the data set returns an incorrect result or null result set.
OB: When I set the filter expression 'row[0] equals to 0', the data set returns an incorrect result or null result set.
EB: I expect to see a relevant error message when an invalid filter expression is set for row[0].
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps: 
1. Set the filter expression as 'row[0] equals to 0' 
2. Execute the data set query 
3. Observe the result returned by the data set
